Scripts for Alpine, Arch, and Void Linux.
=========================================

All scripts, unless otherwise noted at the top of each file,
were written by me. If I have stolen any scripts from others
I've usually preserved the headers and authorship information.

If you see one of your scripts here, and I forgot to give you
credit for the authorship, just let me know with and issue 
and I'll fix it :)

Special thanks to:
	- Dylan Araps (@dylanaraps)
	- Mitch Weaver (@mitchweaver)
